title: Bold free agency predictions, ATN Mailbag!
itunes:title: Bold free agency predictions, ATN Mailbag!
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling -- continues its analysis of free agency, making a raft of bold predictions about how players will perform in their new uniforms. Elsewhere, the gang dips into the mailbag to answer burning questions from ATN Nation.
